{
  "_comment": "Maps CLI actions to upstream endpoints. Format: 'module/endpoint_name' (single) | ['module/ep1','module/ep2'] (fallback chain — first works wins) | {variant: ref} (multi-variant). Fallback chain prevents single-endpoint outages from killing the action.",

